## Recommended Configuration for USDS-M

### Conservative (Recommended for Testing)

```bash
BINANCE_TESTNET=true
TRADING_LEVERAGE=3.0
MAX_DAILY_LOSS_PCT=0.03       # 3% limit (strict)
MAX_DRAWDOWN_PCT=0.05         # 5% limit (strict)
MAX_POSITION_PCT=0.15         # Max 15% per position
KELLY_FRACTION=0.15           # Very conservative
MIN_ORDER_QTY=0.01            # Smaller test trades
```

**Use case:** Testing on mainnet with small amounts before scaling up.

### Moderate (Recommended for Production)

```bash
BINANCE_TESTNET=false
TRADING_LEVERAGE=5.0
MAX_DAILY_LOSS_PCT=0.05       # 5% limit
MAX_DRAWDOWN_PCT=0.10         # 10% limit
MAX_POSITION_PCT=0.25         # Max 25% per position
KELLY_FRACTION=0.25           # Standard Kelly (25% of full)
MIN_ORDER_QTY=0.1
```

**Use case:** Live trading with moderate risk.

### Aggressive (Only After Proven Profitability)

```bash
BINANCE_TESTNET=false
TRADING_LEVERAGE=10.0
MAX_DAILY_LOSS_PCT=0.10       # 10% limit (higher risk)
MAX_DRAWDOWN_PCT=0.20         # 20% limit (higher risk)
MAX_POSITION_PCT=0.40         # Max 40% per position
KELLY_FRACTION=0.50           # 50% of full Kelly
MIN_ORDER_QTY=0.5
```

**Use case:** Only with proven strategy and significant capital.

