## Troubleshooting

### "Insufficient margin" errors

```bash
# Reduce leverage or position size
TRADING_LEVERAGE=3.0
MAX_POSITION_PCT=0.15
```

### Trades not filling on testnet

```bash
# Testnet fills may be simulated; try mainnet paper trading
BINANCE_TESTNET=false
LIVE_MODE=paper
```

### Funding rate concerns

```bash
# Check current funding rate in Binance app
# Set alerts if rate > 0.05% (0.0005)
# Adjust position size if rate is very high
```

### Position size too small

```bash
# Increase min order or reduce leverage
MIN_ORDER_QTY=0.05
# OR
TRADING_LEVERAGE=5.0
```

